Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
set_threshold_voltage_group(25.10)          set_threshold_voltage_group(25.10)

Name
       set_threshold_voltage_group  -  Groups  timing libraries into different
       voltage threshold (Vth) classes (e.g., HVT, LVT, ULVT)

Syntax
       set_threshold_voltage_group

        [-help]

        [-hinst <<string>>]

        -name <<group_name>>

        [-override]

       {-libraries <<library list>> | -lib_cells <<lib cell list>>}

       Groups timing libraries into different voltage threshold (Vth)  classes
       (e.g., HVT, LVT, ULVT).

       This  command can be used to define (or redefine) the threshold voltage
       groups associated with the specified  timing  library  cells.  You  can
       group  entire  libraries  into  a single group, or group by per library
       cell specification.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -hinst <<string>>
              Specifies the hierarchical instances.

       -lib_cells <<lib cell list>>
              Specifies a list of library cells to be defined in the VT group.

       -libraries <<library list>>
              Specifies a list of libraries to be defined in the VT group.

       -name <<group_name>>
              Specifies the name of the threshold voltage group being defined.

       -override
              Allows you to override Liberty defined VT groups.

              If the Liberty timing library already has native threshold_volt-
              age_group attributes at the library or library cell level,  then
              you  can  use  the  -override parameter to customize it with the
              specified threshold voltage group.

Examples
              * The following commands define library threshold voltage groups
                if they do not preexist in the .lib:

                set_threshold_voltage_group   -name   SVT    -libraries   std-
                cell_vt_1p62V_cworst

                set_threshold_voltage_group   -name   LVT    -libraries   std-
                cell_2vt_1p62V_cworst

                set_threshold_voltage_group   -name   ULVT   -libraries   std-
                cell_vlvt_1p62V_cworst

                set_threshold_voltage_group   -name   ELVT   -libraries   std-
                cell_flvt_1p62V_cworst

